{"tid":537372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[開定先]馮小剛-芳華","createTime":"2018-01-22T15:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T06:20:39.000Z","uid":31773,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4015ca81f2cc330534f461f334a1b1de7dfb7075","tid":537372,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"大陸好既導演一向鍾意踩界<br />\n而馮小剛一向都係其中較踩線個個<br />\n呢套芳華係大陸一波三折先上到<br />\n最主要原因係涉及太多敏感體材<br />\n土共唔太願意面對既歷史<br />\n即使電影看似歌頌當年的文工團<br />\n但其實劇情頗為嘲諷<br />\n想深一層幾土共，用完即棄，好人無好報"},{"pid":"b1c404d3452d6d0cbcebb6ea5873be2e054bb11a","tid":537372,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"黎緊就上，好戲真係要支持下"},{"pid":"3574e7b66375dc2db3d8319825c2867306a0f001","tid":537372,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b68b72da14d8183b524125651c74240580a63c","tid":537372,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"呢度睇內地戲會被打成五毛，你快D走我幫你擋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c90541ef42d806fac25f710de542722b5e5c06","tid":537372,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"應該唔太多人會睇呢套"},{"pid":"27e29fb041eaf30bbbc09f5acd25645a53ae2ff2","tid":537372,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b68b72da14d8183b524125651c74240580a63c","tid":537372,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"呢度睇內地戲會被打成五毛，你快D走我幫你擋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總有班人未睇就先判"},{"